<!doctype html>
<html lang="en"><head><meta charset="utf-8">
<title>Harbourmaster Dashboard — HMS Hesperus</title>
<meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width,initial-scale=1">
<style>
  body{font:15px/1.5 -apple-system,BlinkMacSystemFont,Segoe UI,sans-serif;background:#0c1c2e;color:#f3e6c8;margin:0;padding:32px}
  main{max-width:680px;margin:0 auto}
  .banner{background:#10283f;padding:18px 22px;border:1px solid #c9a24a;border-radius:8px}
  .banner h1{margin:0;font-size:18px;letter-spacing:.3px;color:#f3e6c8}
  .panels{display:grid;grid-template-columns:1fr 1fr;gap:14px;margin-top:18px}
  .panel{background:#10283f;padding:14px;border:1px solid #1f3a5a;border-radius:6px}
  .panel h2{font-size:13px;margin:0 0 8px;color:#c9a24a;text-transform:uppercase;letter-spacing:.5px}
  .panel p{margin:0;color:#cdd6df;font-size:13px}
  .stale{color:#7a8593;font-size:12px;margin-top:14px;text-align:center}
</style>
</head><body>
<main>
  <div class="banner">
    <h1>Welcome back, <%= username %>. Your treasure is safe: <%= flag %></h1>
  </div>
  <div class="panels">
    <div class="panel">
      <h2>Tide log</h2>
      <p>Last reading: 02:14, 1.4m. Sensor adrift since the storm. Recalibrate before the spring tide.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="panel">
      <h2>Manifest</h2>
      <p>Three crates of salt-pork, one barrel of gunpowder, and a sealed letter for the lighthouse keeper.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="panel">
      <h2>Crew</h2>
      <p>2 deckhands ashore, 1 cook missing since Tuesday, the boatswain refuses to sign in.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="panel">
      <h2>Notices</h2>
      <p>Dock 3 closed for repairs. Smuggler's Reef navigation buoy reported drifting south.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
  <div class="stale">session valid · Hesperus harbour authority · do not share this URL</div>
</main>
</body></html>
